	<main>
		<section>
			<h2>Registration</h2>
			<p>To register to the E-Voting website, follow these steps:</p>
			<ol>
				<li>Go to the registration page.</li>
				<li>Fill in the required details and click on the 'Register' button.</li>
				<li>You will receive an email with your login credentials.</li>
			</ol>
			<img src="img/screenshot1.jpg" alt="Registration Page">
			<img src="img/screenshot2.jpg" alt="Registration Email">
		</section>
		<section>
			<h2>Verification</h2>
			<p>To verify yourself as an eligible voter, follow these steps:</p>
			<ol>
				<li>Go to the verification page.</li>
				<li>Enter your details and click on the 'Verify' button.</li>
				<li>You will receive a confirmation message on the screen.</li>
			</ol>
			<img src="img/screenshot3.jpg" alt="Verification Page">
		</section>
		<section>
			<h2>Login</h2>
			<p>To login to the E-Voting website, follow these steps:</p>
			<ol>
				<li>Go to the login page.</li>
				<li>Enter your login credentials sent to your email and click on the 'Login' button.</li>
			</ol>
			<img src="img/screenshot4.jpg" alt="Login Page">
		</section>
		<section>
			<h2>Voting</h2>
			<p>To cast your vote, follow these steps:</p>
			<ol>
				<li>Open the voting page through the link sent to your email.</li>
				<li>Select your preferred candidate.</li>
				<li>Click on the 'Submit Vote' button to submit your vote.</li>
				<li>You will receive a confirmation message on the screen.</li>
			</ol>
			<img src="img/screenshot5.jpg" alt="Voting Page">
		</section>
		<section>
			<h2>Contact Us</h2>
			<p>If you have any issues or questions regarding the voting process, please contact us through the 'Contact Us' page.</p>
			<button><a href="contactus">Contact Us</a></button>
		</section>
	</main>
